### 错误处理

```python
from snap7.exceptions import Snap7Exception

try:
    data = client.db_read(db_number, start, size)
except Snap7Exception as e:
    if "Address out of range" in str(e):
        logger.error(f"DB{db_number} 地址越界，检查 size 参数")
